following accounting identities hold: \code{GEXP = DC + FC}, \code{DC = DVA + DDC},
\code{FC = FVA + FDC}, \code{DVA = VAX + REF}, and (exporter/source only)
\code{GVC = GVCB + GVCF = GEXP - DAVAX} and \code{GVCB = FC + DDC}.

